Requirements
Ordbog

1. Create an account
the user can create an account in order to access the system. 
priority: 2

2. recover password
the user can receive an email to recover his/her password
priority: 1

3. create dictionary
the user can select a language
priority:  3

4. create word/phrase
the user can create a word or phrase that contains the following data:
language, word/phrase, definition,picture,place,
priority: 5

5. retrieve all words
the user can retrieve all the words previously saved
 